CD70


Description

CD70 antigen (CD70). Cytokine which is the ligand for CD27. The CD70-CD27 pathway plays an important role in the generation and maintenance of T cell immunity, in particular during antiviral responses.


Clinical trials

NCT02830724 - Breast Cancer, Renal Cell Cancer, Ovarian Cancer, Pancreatic Cancer, Melanoma
